window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Combined for the first time in one volume, here are audiobooks seven-nine of the internationally best-selling The Ghost series: <i>Ghost in the Ashes</i>, <i>Ghost in the Mask</i>, and <i>Ghost in the Surge</i>.</p> <p>Caina Amalas is a nightfighter of the Ghosts, the spies and assassins of the Emperor of Nighmar, and through cunning and valor she has cast down both proud lords and mighty sorcerers.</p> <p>But a power darker than any she has ever faced is awakening.</p> <p>When a mad assassin armed with a sorcerous blade rampages through the Emperor's capital, Caina must track the weapon to its origin, a ruined city blighted by the folly of sorcerers, a city that holds weapons far more potent than mere blades.</p> <p>Weapons that can resurrect an ancient empire of dark sorcery to enslave the world anew...</p>"; 
